        {
            "title": "債券交易員不再押注聯儲會2026年降息一次的概率為100%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 債券交易員已不再押注聯儲會在2026年降息的概率為100%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與聯儲會政策會議日期掛鉤的利率互換合約顯示，交易員周四押注的今年降息幅度僅為24個基點，這相當於進行一次幅度為25個基點降息的可能性不到100%。周三晚些時候，交易員押注的降息幅度約為30個基點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一轉變正值美國國債延續近期跌勢，其中對聯儲會政策變化最為敏感的兩年期國債殖利率上漲4個基點，接近3.70%。本周，由於投資者擔心中東衝突將持續推高能源價格，導致通膨再度抬頭，美國國債承壓。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0f8661d8-98d2-3fb6-b5ca-975ccea3a810-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，本周各公司大量發行新債，同時美國財政部將於紐約時間下午1點發行220億美元的30年期國債。本周早些時候的3年期和10年期國債標售遇疲軟需求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Traders Are No Longer Fully Pricing In a Fed Rate Cut This Year</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%832026%E5%B9%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-%E6%AC%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E7%82%BA100-151833300.html",
