        {
            "title": "富國銀行下調Conagra、Campbell’s和General Mills評級,警告獲利風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 富國銀行週四在一份報告中將Conagra Brands、Campbell’s Company和<span>General Mills</span>的股票評級下調至減持,警告稱盈利壓力、高槓桿率以及股息支付率偏高的組合,使這些公司面臨表現不佳的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Chris Carey表示,此次下調評級反映了\"每股盈利風險、高槓桿率和緊張的股息支付率的匯聚\",並認為這種組合\"儘管估值和市場情緒處於低位,但可能導致相對同業表現不佳\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-98cd0422-b296-3c4a-a24c-ceecd159361d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">富國銀行對Campbell’s的2027財年每股盈利預測較市場預期低10%,Conagra低9%,<span><span>General Mills</span></span>低6%,並預計到2027年這三家公司的槓桿率都將超過4倍,為其覆蓋範圍內的最高水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該銀行全面下調了目標價,將Conagra的目標價下調至15美元,Campbell’s下調至20美元,General Mills下調至35美元,均基於2027年的盈利倍數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Carey指出,消費趨勢疲軟、\"通脹持續攀升\"以及銷售、一般和行政費用預算緊張,是2027財年面臨的額外壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他補充說,\"槓桿率和股息支付率正接近仍可控但肯定令人不安的水平\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管承認一些投資者可能認為近期的疲軟已經消化了壞消息,但富國銀行警告稱,該板塊\"可能正進入另一個每股盈利面臨風險且槓桿率高企的財年\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過,Carey也強調了上行風險,包括夏季消費改善、通脹緩解或成本節約提升,但他認為負面因素更有可能占主導地位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%8C%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFconagra-campbell-s%E5%92%8Cgeneral-mills%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A9%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-143850415.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-12 23:05:18",
